    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Rear Door Glass Protection Screen</title>
        <para>The rear lower door window protection screen is an available option. This screen protects the lower rear
            door window from damage from items that may cause damage to the lower door glass. To remove the lower door
            window glass screen:
        </para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Locate the mounting screws (
                <hotlnk document="s47003_23.xml" xrefid="f4700371">Figure 71, Item 4</hotlnk>) around the perimeter of
                the screen assembly and attachment clips, loosen and remove the screws and clips.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the screen.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcsubproc>
